<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zilla+Slab:ital,wght@1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
      }
      /* header */
      .fixed-header {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #fff;
        z-index: 1000;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .header-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 10px 20px;
      }

      .header-wrapper h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #444;
      }

      .button a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
      }

      main {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      /* main container */
      .containers {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: start;
      }
      /* footer style */
      footer {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
        padding: 10px;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: -2px -1px 4px 0px rgb(0 0 0);
      }
      .button button:hover,
      .button a:hover {
        background-color: #17a2b8;
      }
      /* features style */
      .containers {
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background-color: #fff;
      }

      .containers h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .containers ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .containers ul li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .containers ul li:before {
        content: "•";
        margin-right: 10px;
        color: #007bff;
      }

      .containers ul li:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      /* for routes http styles */
      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        width: 100%;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      th, td {
        text-align: left;
        padding: 8px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }

      th {
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: white;
      }

      tr:nth-child(even) {
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }

      tr:hover {
        background-color: #ddd;
      }

      td:first-child {
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      /* setup style */
      .setup-containers {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .setup-instructions {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .setup-list {
        margin-left: 5px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      .setup-list li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .heading{
        font-size: 15px;
        font-family: Verdana;
        color: #2c3e50;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .underline{
        text-decoration: underline !important;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 2rem 0;
      }
      .footer-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .footer-text {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Zilla Slab', serif;
      }

      .footer-icons {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .footer-icons a {
        margin-left: 1rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="fixed-header">
      <div class="header-wrapper">
        <h1>Polling System API</h1>
        <div class="button">
          <span class="heading">For More Information Please</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/Saurabhdixit93/PollingSystem_Api-Using-NodeJs" target="_blank">Visit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class="containers" style=" margin-top: 10rem;margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <strong class="underline">Vist Gihub Repository to read on How to use this API.</strong>
        <p>
          API where anyone can create questions with options and also add votes to it and you can easily create engaging and interactive polling experiences.
        </p>
        <br>
        <br>
        <div class="containers">
          <h2 class="underline">Features</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Create a question (Add as many questions as you want)</li>
            <li>Add options to a question</li>
            <li>Add a vote to an option of question</li>
            <li>Delete a question → (Note : A question can’t be deleted if one of it’s options has votes)</li>
            <li>Delete an option → (Note : An option can’t be deleted if it has even one vote given to it)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <br>
        <strong class="setup-instructions underline">Routes and its methods:</strong>
        <br>
        <br>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <th>HTTP Method</th>
            <th>Route</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>POST</td>
            <td>/questions/create</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>POST</td>
            <td>/questions/:id/options/create</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>DELETE</td>
            <td>/questions/:id/delete</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>DELETE</td>
            <td>/options/:id/delete</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>PUT</td>
            <td>/options/:id/add_vote</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>GET</td>
            <td>/questions/:id</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <br>
        <div class="setup-containers">
          <p class="setup-instructions underline">How to set up the project:</p>
          <ol class="setup-list">
            <li>Clone the project onto your local machine.</li>
            <li>Run 'npm install' to install required dependencies.</li>
            <li>Run 'npm start' in terminal to start server.</li>
            <li>Visit your app at http://localhost:4000.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="footer-content">
          <p class="footer-text">devloped By<span style="color: #007bff;"> Saurabh Dixit </span>© 2023 Polling System API.</p>
          <div class="footer-icons">
            <strong>Contact </strong>
            <a style="text-decoration: none;"  href="https://github.com/Saurabhdixit93" target="_blank">
              <img src="https://img.icons8.com/3d-fluency/30/null/github.png" alt="">
            </a>
            <a style="text-decoration: none;"  href="https://linkedin.com/in/Saurabhdixit93" target="_blank">
              <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/30/null/linkedin-2--v1.png" alt="">
            </a>
            <a style="text-decoration: none;"  href="mailto:smartds2550@gmail.com">
              <img src="https://img.icons8.com/3d-fluency/30/null/gmail.png" alt="">
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
